Summary: UFO cought while taking photos of the moon
divs: Sighting DetailsI took a picture of the moon on a cloudy night sky and again after tweaking the setting on the camera. Days later I downloaded the photos to my laptop to see what looks like an UFO is on the first (cloudy) photo to the lower right side.
